cs.SE, cs.HC, cs.PL, cs.SD, cs.IR 

The paper discusses the issue of bug reporting in mobile and GUI-based applications, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The focus on mobile and GUI-based applications suggests a potential overlap with human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and programming languages (cs.PL) sub-categories. The proposed research program also involves examining the impact of new bug reporting mechanisms, which could involve software design (cs.SD) and information retrieval (cs.IR) techniques.
